		<title>MiCA Decoded: &#8216;We Have an EU Office&#8217; Is Not Enough: Here&#8217;s What Regulators Actually Want to See</title>
		<link>https://news.bitcoin.com/mica-decoded-we-have-an-eu-office-is-not-enough-heres-what-regulators-actually-want-to-see/</link>
		
